entries.content: This entire session remains unissued and the masters no longer exist. Ledger shows 14 men, 3t; 3tb; 4s; p; g; b; d. The title "Jumpy" would be later assigned to Chatterbox. Jumpy recorded on this date may or may not be the same song as Chatterbox.
